I need assistance from the L3 team regarding the following case.
&nbsp;
Case Summary:
A customer on the $9 Starter plan has reported that fallback rates are being displayed at checkout instead of calculated rates.
&nbsp;
Details:
We reviewed the app settings, carrier accounts, automation rules, and shipping zones, and everything appears to be configured correctly. We were also able to replicate the scenario while placing test orders.
&nbsp;
From the logs, the rates are being returned successfully. However, for the same order, the calculated rates are not consistently displayed at checkout, and fallback rates are shown instead.
&nbsp;
I have attached a short video demonstrating the entire process.
&nbsp;
Additional Information:
  This behavior appears to be intermittent. The customer reported that out of three attempts, it failed twice.  The customer would like to ensure that calculated rates are displayed consistently to avoid any potential shipping loss.  &nbsp;
Expected Result:
Calculated rates should be displayed at checkout consistently.
